{
  "stem": "6878.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he says, go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't had anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I had in that boot 32,000 rubles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And if you would believe it, that I brought in into the ghetto a gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The caretaker, I ask her if she can find me a gun, because I decided, seeing that our people are getting slaughtered by the day, if they will come in to take me or my kid or my wife, I will pull out the gun and shoot them first, and then get shot myself.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she, she organized for me a gun, a 9-millimeter gun, that's-- the bullet is quite the heavy one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I pinned that, that gun under my leather little jacket what I had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I come up to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the officer in charge there, the German, said, open up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should open up my, my jacket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I opened up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he just did this to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Go in.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had a gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they find on me a gun, find on me the gun, I would have be shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My wife, my kid, they would have be shot straightaway, if they found the gun, because-- And then, the story with the gun, when I brought in the gun, I didn't say to Ida that I'm going in-- I'm bringing a gun.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I just brought and-- and she couldn't sleep nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She start to nag me, get rid of the gun, because if they find a gun in [INAUDIBLE], was, the law was to shoot out everybody from the surroundings if they find ammunition on somebody.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she nagged me to such a state that I came, I took the gun into the toilet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I threw him into-- the toilets used to be outside, a hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
